dataTableRowDataDTO Data Type

Contains all of the data related to a table row on an incident

Namespace
(Default)
Properties
name data type type namespace min/max occurs description
actions actionInfoDTO element 0/unbounded The list of actions available to the caller for execution.
cells (custom) element 0/1 The mapping of column->cell data for the row. The mapping key can be specified using all names or all ids.
id int element 0/1 The internal ID of the row. This can be used to update a single row in a table. This value is read-only.

Example

<dataTableRowDataDTO>
  <id>...</id>
  <cells>...</cells>
  <actions>
    <id>...</id>
    <name>...</name>
    <enabled>...</enabled>
  </actions>
</dataTableRowDataDTO>
